name: knSgmrTrnr
description:
Hi guys!

This is an embedding that inspired by a vintage Pokemon trainer style.

If you wanna test it, you can put this word on the prompt: art by knSgmrTrnr

And I suggest this negative prompts: Deformed, blurry, bad anatomy, disfigured, poorly drawn face, mutation, mutated, extra limb, ugly, poorly drawn hands, missing limb, blurry, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, malformed hands, blur, out of focus, long neck, long body, ((((mutated hands and fingers)))), (((out of frame)))

This model only works on SD 1.5 .

if you wanna support me, you can buy me a coffee: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/elrivx
